<SLUG> BC-CANDY-CORN-HNS </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
CANDY CORN REMAINS THE KING OF SWEET 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by New York Times News Service clients.)  
 By DANIEL J. VARGAS  
 c.1998 San Antonio Express-News  
