districts are up for grabs. The campaigns are made more interesting
by the conservative leanings of the Democrats in three out of the
four contests. We'll spend time with Republican Gex (pronounced
Jay) Williams and Democrat Ken Lucas, who are locked in a tight
race. Williams is a client of Georgia's Ralph Reed. (Sherman,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
</P>
<P>
