 This ``separate buy'' article is from Latin Trade magazine,
America's leading journal of Latin American business, finance and
trade: &HT;    SPINNING GOLD. While the textiles industry lags in Brazil, it's
booming in Mexico and the rest of Central America and the
Caribbean.
 &HT;    Filed as BC-BOOM-BUST-TEXTILES-LATINTRADE-NYTSF.
