<P>
   CLINTON-ADS (Washington) _ While the Republicans are launching
$10 million ad blitz about the White House sex scandal, President
Clinton says he has atoned for his extramarital relationship with
Monica Lewinsky and reiterates that he will focus on national
issues. By STEWART M. POWELL. (Also will be filed in the ``p''
category.)
