<P>
   TRIPLE _ ATLANTA _ Atlanta Police officers called police in
Florida to ask them to seal the apartment of Gerrold Shropshire
after he was shot to death in the Atlanta Hilton &AMP; Towers, so they
did. Then, several days later, someone broke into the apartment and
threw things around, but didn't appear to steal anything. Seeking
