<HEADLINE>
NEW GOP AD PORTRAYS SCHUMER AS FLIP-FLOPPING ON VOTES 
</HEADLINE>
   (EDS: Also filed in national news, ``a,'' category)  
 (For use by New York Times News Service clients.)  
