<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-ILL-GOV-RACE-800&AMP;ADD-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
GOVERNOR'S RACE DRAWS LITTLE INTEREST IN CHICAGO, BOOSTING
REPUBLICAN 
</HEADLINE>
  (DUPLICATION WARNING: Also moving in the ``a'' news file.) 
(nk) 
 By DIRK JOHNSON    
 c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
