</P>
<P>
   NY-PATAKI-PROFILE (Undated) _ Gov. George Pataki has made a
career of being underestimated, and a habit of defying
expectations. And in the four years since his election, he has done
just that, with considerable success. By Richard Perez-Pena.
(Scheduled to move by 9 p.m. ET in ``p'' news file.)
</P>
<P>
   BKN-NBA-LABOR (Undated) _ Developments in the NBA labor
situation. By Mike Wise. (Scheduled to move by 9 p.m. ET in ``s''
news file.)
</P>
