<SLUG> BC-REED-KY-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Reed doesn't shy from controversy
 &HT;    By Mark Sherman
 &HT;    c. 1998 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
