<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-TEX-POWERDEREG-CALIF-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Californians take a wait-and-see attitude
 &HT;    (With TEX-POWERDEREG, TEX-POWERDEREG-SUMMARY,
TEX-POWERDEREG-PENN. Photos available. For Sun., Nov. 1. Moving on
a and financial wires.)
 &HT;    By Bruce Hight
 &HT;    c. 1998 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
