<HEADLINE>
END OF STRAIGHT-TICKET VOTING MAY BACKFIRE ON ILLINOIS GOP 
</HEADLINE>
   (DUPLICATION NOTICE: Also sent in category `a')  
(See also ILL-GOV-RACE) 
(bl) 
 By DIRK JOHNSON   
 c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
