A2362 &Cx1f; taf-z
u w &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-ATTACK-ADS-ART-NYT &LR;      10-28 0622
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-ATTACK-ADS-ART-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
GOOD-GOVERNMENT GROUP FIGHTS ATTACK ADS WITH ONE OF ITS OWN 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (ATTN: Pa.)  (DUPLICATION NOTICE: Also sent in category `p') 
(ART ADV: Photo is being sent to NYT photo clients. Non-subscribers
can make individual purchase by calling (888) 603-1036 or (888)
346-9867.) 
(nk) 
