<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-10-28 20:29 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2404 &Cx1f; tad-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-TRIPLE29-COX     10-28 1142
