chock-full-of-chuckles gala. (Sara Krulwich/New York Times Photo)
</P>
<P>
   (NYT23) NEW YORK -- Oct. 28, 1998 -- ISRAEL-FILMS, 10-28 -- Amos
Gitai, director of ``Day After Day,'' part of the Israeli film
festival. ``This is not a society that is outlined or completely
