<HEADLINE>
HISPANIC LEADERS ASSAIL VACCO OVER INTERVIEW 
</HEADLINE>
  (Duplication warning: Also filed in ``p'' category.) 
(mk) 
 By ALAN FINDER   
 c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   NEW YORK _ Editors of a weekly newspaper say state Attorney
